[msg msg003_MSG]
[f 0 5 65278][f 2 1]If armor has a status ailment bonus, it[n]increases your resistance to that ailment.[n][f 1 1][e]

[msg msg004_MSG]
[f 0 5 65278][f 2 1]Status-increasing effects raise your stats,[n]whether they be from weapons or armor.[n][f 1 1][e]

[msg msg005_MSG]
[f 0 5 65278][f 2 1]Weapons with piercing or splash effects [n]can hit multiple targets.[n][f 1 1][e]

